paragraphs.title: Create External Table
paragraphs.text:
%script

--------------------------------------------
-- Create External Table Reference
--------------------------------------------

BEGIN
    DBMS_CLOUD.CREATE_EXTERNAL_TABLE(
        table_name =>'FEMA_CLAIMS_EXT',
        credential_name =>'OBJ_STORE_CRED',
        file_uri_list =>'https://swiftobjectstorage.us-ashburn-1.oraclecloud.com/v1/gse00014467/ADWC_DEMO/FEMA_Assistance_Claims.csv',
        format => '{"delimiter" : ",",
                "skipheaders" : "1" ,
                "blankasnull" : "true" ,
                "removequotes" : "true" ,
                "ignoremissingcolumns" : "true",
                "conversionerrors" : "store_null",
                "trimspaces" : "rtrim",
                "escape" : "true"}',
        column_list => '
            DISASTER NUMBER(38,0), 
            STATE VARCHAR2(26 BYTE), 
            COUNTY VARCHAR2(26 BYTE), 
            CITY VARCHAR2(128 BYTE), 
            ZIP_CODE NUMBER(38,0), 
            VALID_REGISTRATIONS NUMBER(38,0), 
            AVERAGE_FEMA_INSPECTED_DAMAGE NUMBER(38,0),  
            TOTAL_INSPECTED NUMBER(38,0), 
            TOTAL_DAMAGE NUMBER(38,0), 
            NO_FEMA_INSPECTED_DAMAGE NUMBER(38,0), 
            FEMA_INSPECTED_DAMAGE_BETWEEN_1_10K NUMBER(38,0), 
            FEMA_INSPECTED_DAMAGE_BETWEEN_10K_20K NUMBER(38,0), 
            FEMA_INSPECTED_DAMAGE_BETWEEN_20K_30K NUMBER(38,0), 
            FEMA_INSPECTED_DAMAGE_GT_30K NUMBER(38,0), 
            APPROVED_FOR_FEMA_ASSISTANCE NUMBER(38,0), 
            TOTAL_APPROVED_IHP_AMOUNT  NUMBER(38,0), 
            REPAIR_REPLACE_AMOUNT NUMBER(38,0), 
            RENTAL_AMOUNT NUMBER(38,0)
        '
     );
END;
/

%sql

select * 
from 
    (select city, sum(total_damage) as sum_damage 
     from FEMA_CLAIMS_EXT 
     group by city
     order by sum_damage desc)
where sum_damage > 50000000;

paragraphs.title: Performance Scaling
paragraphs.text:
%sql

select sum(lo_extendedprice * lo_discount) as revenue
from ssb.lineorder, ssb.dwdate
where lo_orderdate = d_datekey
and d_yearmonthnum = 199401
and lo_discount between 2 and 8
and lo_quantity between 21 and 35 
and ROWNUM < 500000;

%md
### Takes too long? Scale up for more power.
